1092d8ab-c8bc-4f99-8a8f-afd3a3736c3f.title: Guild Wars 2
1092d8ab-c8bc-4f99-8a8f-afd3a3736c3f.summary: Guild Wars 2 is an award-winning online roleplaying game with fast-paced action combat, deep character customization, and no subscription fee required. Choose from an arsenal of professions and weapons, explore a vast open world, compete in PVP modes and more. Join over 16 million players now!
